# Liabilities Insurance Policy Gross Excluding Current Bonus Amount

## identifier
de4146

## type
float

## definition
Report the total gross policy liability as per prudential standards, excluding current year bonuses. Note that this differs to the accounting standards treatment.

Report amounts gross of ceded reinsurance but inclusive of inwards reinsurance.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Insurance.PolicyGrossExcludingCurrentBonus.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.04
- period=instant
